---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/services.css';
---

<Layout title="HR Services — ClimbHQ" description="HR packages for climbing centres — from compliance basics to full people management, helping you create a great place to work from £249/month." bodyClass="page-hr">

<section class="service-hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(200deg, #071F33 20%, rgba(47, 36, 27, 0.78) 80%), url('/images/bg/hr-services-hero.webp'); background-position: 0px 32%;">
  <div class="service-hero-inner">
    <h1>HR Services</h1>
    <p>People — They're our most important asset…</p>
    <p>It's difficult to give a number for how many pieces of employment legislation there is in the UK. We can all agree that there is a lot!</p>
    <p>We've designed packages that support you creating an amazing place to work, where team members know they are looked after and treated fairly.</p>
    <p>Bespoke services are provided on request — Get in touch today to find out more!</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pricing-section">
  <div class="pricing-grid">
    <div class="pricing-card">
      <h2>Basics</h2>
      <p class="pricing-amount">£249 per month</p>
      <div class="pricing-card-body">
        <p><strong>Policy Formulation and Compliance</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>HR Policy Development: Basic policy templates and customisation</li>
          <li>Quarterly Compliance Monitoring:</li>
          <li>Annual risk assessment</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>HR Technology Solutions</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Time and Attendance Tracking: Basic attendance tracking system</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Virtual HR Assistant</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>24/7 Q&amp;A</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-card featured">
      <h2>Essentials</h2>
      <p class="pricing-amount">£449 per month</p>
      <div class="pricing-card-body">
        <p><strong>Everything in Basics and</strong></p>
        <p><strong>Advisory Services</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>5 hours of HR Consultancy</li>
          <li>Access to essential advice:</li>
          <li>Recruitment Support: Job description templates and posting guidance</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Training and Development</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Training Programs: Access to our standard training library</li>
          <li>Performance Reviews: templates and guidance</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Emergency Response</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Crisis Management: Response planning and support</li>
          <li>Health and Safety Training: Annual safety protocol refresher training</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-card">
      <h2>Complete</h2>
      <p class="pricing-amount">£949 per month</p>
      <div class="pricing-card-body">
        <p><strong>Everything in Essentials and</strong></p>
        <p><strong>Policy Formulation and Compliance</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Fully customised policies with implementation support</li>
          <li>Monthly compliance reviews and updates</li>
          <li>Quarterly risk assessments with detailed mitigation strategies</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Advisory Services</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Up to 15 hours of monthly consultation</li>
          <li>Recruitment Support: Full recruitment cycle management, including candidate screening</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Workplace Culture and Engagement</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Employee Engagement: Custom engagement initiatives and implementation</li>
          <li>Diversity and Inclusion: Comprehensive D&amp;I strategy development</li>
          <li>Tailored wellness program design and implementation</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Training and Development</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Custom training development and delivery</li>
          <li>Unlimited access to our extended learning resources</li>
          <li>Quarterly performance review system with coaching</li>
        </ul>
        <p>HR Technology Solutions</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Full HRIS setup and integration</li>
          <li>Advanced scheduling and attendance management</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Emergency Response</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Crisis Management: response planning and support</li>
          <li>Quarterly safety training and certification support</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="service-addons">
  <div class="service-addons-inner">
    <p>Packages are monthly, per site</p>
    <p><strong>Add-On Services</strong></p>
    <p>Customise your plan with these additional services:</p>
    <p><strong>On-Site HR Support:</strong> £300/day</p>
    <p><strong>Employee Satisfaction Survey:</strong> £575/annually</p>
    <p><strong>Team Building Event:</strong> Starting at £700</p>
    <p><strong>Advanced Leadership Training:</strong> £950/program</p>
    <p>All plans include a dedicated HR consultant - Contact us today to find out more</p>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .pricing-card-body p {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 16px 0 8px;
  }
  .pricing-card-body p strong {
    color: #5ED4F5;
  }
  .pricing-card-body ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }
  .pricing-card-body li {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #9796A3;
    padding: 4px 0 4px 20px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .pricing-card-body li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #5ED4F5;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
</style>
